WEBVTT

00:02:59.833 --> 00:03:02.559
My work as a cartoonist
became more and more of a nuisance

00:03:02.583 --> 00:03:03.934
for the dictatorship.

00:03:03.958 --> 00:03:06.684
They have no tolerance
for any freedom of expression

00:03:06.708 --> 00:03:08.125
or free thinking.

00:03:08.833 --> 00:03:12.458
(Speaks Spanish)

00:03:25.625 --> 00:03:26.893
After I got fired,

00:03:26.917 --> 00:03:29.559
I started to feel unsafe
in my own country.

00:03:29.583 --> 00:03:32.476
I received anonymous calls
and death threats.